points in today's early going. Advancers and decliners are evenly 
mixed on the New York Stock Exchange. 
</P>
<P>
	The Nasdaq Composite Index is up three points and the S&AMP;P 500  
Index is up less than a point. 
</P>
<P>
	The Nasdaq composite index is down 9.6 percent from the record  
