<HEADLINE> AP Corrects Celebrex-Viagra Story </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
	NEW YORK (AP) -- In a story comparing the sales of Viagra and  
Celebrex, The Associated Press erroneously reported on Aug. 3 that 
Pfizer manufactures both drugs. 
</P>
<P>
	Monsanto manufactures Celebrex and markets it jointly with  
Pfizer; Pfizer makes and distributes Viagra. 
</P>
